*ccp4-6.0.1 (16 Jun 2006)

  16 Jun 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  +files/6.0.1-dont-make-dirs-in-configure.patch,
  +files/6.0.1-ppc-double-define-gerror.patch,
  +files/ccp4i-default-to-firefox.patch,
